{"id": "ChIJg0sqGAi8woAR0yftsSICivQ", "rating": 4.1, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 401, "displayName": {"text": "Go Greek Yogurt", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJg0sqGAi8woAR0yftsSICivQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkWFpFUktOakZLWlZOSlNGaHFjRmRFU21wR1JFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Nice yogurt shop. It seems most go for the froyo.\n\nI noticed the yogurt flavors in the case, and some of the flavors looked interesting, like rose, sour cherry, and hazelnut. If I were hungry, which I wasn't at the time of my visit, I would've tried one.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Nice yogurt shop. It seems most go for the froyo.\n\nI noticed the yogurt flavors in the case, and some of the flavors looked interesting, like rose, sour cherry, and hazelnut. If I were hungry, which I wasn't at the time of my visit, I would've tried one.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "__", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100584301031568188407/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVabfXfTDag5scaBV5fd9DB289fxs9xEeyY1O1PeIxLxp6KRJj5NQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-15T02:52:08.393937422Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkWFpFUktOakZLWlZOSlNGaHFjRmRFU21wR1JFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkWFpFUktOakZLWlZOSlNGaHFjRmRFU21wR1JFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bc08182a4b83:0xf48a0222b1ed27d3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJg0sqGAi8woAR0yftsSICivQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKblgwSk5Sbmt5WW1Wa2VEQjBWa3d4TlUwNWFtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "very good Greek yogurt, many flavors, and great service. It's very crowded always, but the line moves quickly. And a big shout out and thanks to their amazing staff! who always bag the yogurt with a lot of ice whenever I ask for it so that it stays cool on the drive home", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "very good Greek yogurt, many flavors, and great service. It's very crowded always, but the line moves quickly. And a big shout out and thanks to their amazing staff! who always bag the yogurt with a lot of ice whenever I ask for it so that it stays cool on the drive home", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Cyrus Azad", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100359949451982223374/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMNqbvKkpWi0jLo2KZQWNZ_gs3yLF7X8M_AcFTWSduHG7nzw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-12T06:38:05.832688710Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKblgwSk5Sbmt5WW1Wa2VEQjBWa3d4TlUwNWFtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKblgwSk5Sbmt5WW1Wa2VEQjBWa3d4TlUwNWFtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bc08182a4b83:0xf48a0222b1ed27d3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJg0sqGAi8woAR0yftsSICivQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xackxXOW9SRGQ2Y0RCTWNqRnNiVGwwVVVzelJuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "If you’re on the hunt for a delightful yogurt experience, this place is definitely worth a visit! The staff here is incredibly friendly and always ready to make your visit enjoyable. While the yogurt itself is quite tasty, what truly sets this spot apart is the wide variety of toppings they offer. Whether you’re in the mood for something fruity, crunchy, or a little bit of everything, you’re sure to find something that tickles your fancy. It’s a fun and inviting place to satisfy your yogurt cravings!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "If you’re on the hunt for a delightful yogurt experience, this place is definitely worth a visit! The staff here is incredibly friendly and always ready to make your visit enjoyable. While the yogurt itself is quite tasty, what truly sets this spot apart is the wide variety of toppings they offer. Whether you’re in the mood for something fruity, crunchy, or a little bit of everything, you’re sure to find something that tickles your fancy. It’s a fun and inviting place to satisfy your yogurt cravings!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Raphael Sebban", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105946374771820544569/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhLS3us9zBSxrKZb7ot9lubMuNmojynjAEpzVgkVh-OmxjFEQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-14T22:23:47.913251496Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xackxXOW9SRGQ2Y0RCTWNqRnNiVGwwVVVzelJuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xackxXOW9SRGQ2Y0RCTWNqRnNiVGwwVVVzelJuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bc08182a4b83:0xf48a0222b1ed27d3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJg0sqGAi8woAR0yftsSICivQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGTVVXRTFVVnBqTkhSVGRXeEhiRXg0WWxoNmQwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "My friends and I came here and ended up leaving completely frustrated. We arrived about 30 minutes before closing and waited patiently in line like everyone else. Right as it became our turn to finally get frozen yogurt, a staff member came from outside and escorted a group of about six loud teenage boys straight to the machines, allowing them to cut the entire line.\n\nNot only were they allowed to skip everyone waiting, but the employee personally filled all of their cups while the rest of us stood there watching. By the time they were done, the yogurt machines were totally empty, leaving actual paying customers with little to nothing after waiting all that time. The boys then loaded up on toppings and walked out acting like they owned the place.\n\nWhen customers understandably expressed frustration, one employee rolled her eyes and said, “It’s five minutes before close,” completely ignoring the fact that many of us had already been waiting long before that.\n\nWhat made the situation worse was the complete lack of professionalism. There appeared to be no adult supervision whatsoever, just a group of teenagers seemingly prioritizing their friends over customers. This place already has a reputation for attracting rowdy, entitled teens, but seeing the staff actively encourage and participate in that behavior was honestly shocking.\n\nI understand closing time can be stressful, but this was incredibly unprofessional and disrespectful to paying customers. Unfortunately, I won’t be coming back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My friends and I came here and ended up leaving completely frustrated. We arrived about 30 minutes before closing and waited patiently in line like everyone else. Right as it became our turn to finally get frozen yogurt, a staff member came from outside and escorted a group of about six loud teenage boys straight to the machines, allowing them to cut the entire line.\n\nNot only were they allowed to skip everyone waiting, but the employee personally filled all of their cups while the rest of us stood there watching. By the time they were done, the yogurt machines were totally empty, leaving actual paying customers with little to nothing after waiting all that time. The boys then loaded up on toppings and walked out acting like they owned the place.\n\nWhen customers understandably expressed frustration, one employee rolled her eyes and said, “It’s five minutes before close,” completely ignoring the fact that many of us had already been waiting long before that.\n\nWhat made the situation worse was the complete lack of professionalism. There appeared to be no adult supervision whatsoever, just a group of teenagers seemingly prioritizing their friends over customers. This place already has a reputation for attracting rowdy, entitled teens, but seeing the staff actively encourage and participate in that behavior was honestly shocking.\n\nI understand closing time can be stressful, but this was incredibly unprofessional and disrespectful to paying customers. Unfortunately, I won’t be coming back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "A", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102973387215678572007/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIS5PLOBs44PQxw9UnhnxwIQ0-i3BkWHwbB4TxE7m7azZ37NA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-19T00:05:08.184245347Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGTVVXRTFVVnBqTkhSVGRXeEhiRXg0WWxoNmQwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pGTVVXRTFVVnBqTkhSVGRXeEhiRXg0WWxoNmQwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bc08182a4b83:0xf48a0222b1ed27d3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJg0sqGAi8woAR0yftsSICivQ/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNYLXNDeDVRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I stopped by to pick up a birthday gift from their loyalty program. The yogurt was yummy, and the friendly server made my experience even better. The $10 birthday gift can purchase around half a bowl of frozen yogurt and some toppings. I think their $11 greek yogurt is more worth it but I didn’t order that. A great spot for delicious Greek yogurt and ice cream in Beverly Hills.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I stopped by to pick up a birthday gift from their loyalty program. The yogurt was yummy, and the friendly server made my experience even better. The $10 birthday gift can purchase around half a bowl of frozen yogurt and some toppings. I think their $11 greek yogurt is more worth it but I didn’t order that. A great spot for delicious Greek yogurt and ice cream in Beverly Hills.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Fang Phattha", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105898268180831740347/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX462pjhsgBgBRaPTJgfFeF9eRc0tpcJZI7Z9WFe8v757sdqRFm=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2024-10-15T16:51:13.085829Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNYLXNDeDVRRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNYLXNDeDVRRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bc08182a4b83:0xf48a0222b1ed27d3"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJg0sqGAi8woAR0yftsSICivQ/photos/AWCwydhS0TW2USgsIJZft260cP3WWJyhgjw8CjHrhcE7j9QmY0Q9Zh3lQu_e9ujfi9m8QH7aK2hj8sl1WM7a9kI-aEcZWECqwy8C4jaiVO1CRnLqL40NKPHyfQzuRucThLk15pazpx_3vPrcMxgMs5mHtIA02tMRGX65O8ULvNVfh95WgP5FC2RIEGE15zZGcVIFtZMbrC8GIOWQ_QHIf6FJYwR1avPoKav4s_ylpbF_g1wLmZuoPsBHE4bHRzzmX2QDysV8ANWZdewtxF9Wp0QxTZTlaEqctCZ6meVnQitLAnwx6p6igL95rQWf7K-LgA4RFrJMNREinjOHVFiRaFOPetMA0NM9japjGVfVDC9N6ML9LlFENmVSL711f72Y9qrJBCXpn_YGXA4LNjiHAyBMj219KsKYJMJcqwdZ_cSjar689sSiCgcejbdF9Wp_FQ", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3600, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "__", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/100584301031568188407", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVabfXfTDag5scaBV5fd9DB289fxs9xEeyY1O1PeIxLxp6KRJj5NQ=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhBGnAimyxOJEUhqIkgtDx8B&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIABIhBGnAimyxOJEUhqIkgtDx8B!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80c2bc08182a4b83:0xf48a0222b1ed27d3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJg0sqGAi8woAR0yftsSICivQ/photos/AWCwydhwrOjgXpt_Ih7Cai6biHYmu0fY_il7JJzqCvoF3tG6p5p0n-VvNvkEisbBf8l_iq9araUDuaFLwnIwDvi5kzGuTeql1-vwM9yRNLPU_WgfUslsvjdo8ncYV1Y-vyfZd4